        void onLoad(java.lang.String pkg,
          PResources res)
        Called when a package's resources are loaded.
        Any resource replacements you want to do have to be done from this callback.
        Parameters:
        pkg - The name of the package. Can be ElPollo.Resources.SYSTEM or an installed package.
        res - The resources belonging to the package.
